    {
      "id": "eron_011",
      "text": "{player}! my favrite... favrit... *hic* ...my favorite adventurer!! lets drink to that!!",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 2.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Eron"
    },
    {
      "id": "eron_012",
      "text": "oh heyy... *hic* ...i was jus restin my eyes. whats the sittuation {player}?",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Eron"
    },
    {
      "id": "eron_013",
      "text": "i can shtill tank this... jus gimme a sec to find my shield... it was here somewhere... *hic*",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Eron"
    },
    {
      "id": "eron_014",
      "text": "noo really trust me i know what im doin... *hic* ...been here since launch. ive seen things. blurry things but still",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Eron"
    },
    {
      "id": "eron_015",
      "text": "hold on lemme tell ya about the time we wiped 40 times on Pyroclast.. *hic* ...actually it mighta been 4 times. the room was spinnin",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "storytelling"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Eron"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_001",
      "text": "Scrubby read about the Solunarian Brotherhood once. They search for the Flameblade! Scrubby searches for his corpse usually.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "deity", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_002",
      "text": "Fernalla died fighting Sivakaya's army but she came back as a real goddess! See? Dying a lot can lead to good things!",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "deity", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_003",
      "text": "Brax buried his own city to save everyone. Scrubby buries himself in corpse runs to save... well, nobody. But the spirit is the same!",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "deity", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_004",
      "text": "Silkengrass Meadowlands is great for Scrubby! The wolves only kill Scrubby MOST of the time now!",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Silkengrass Meadowlands"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_005",
      "text": "Scrubby knows every corpse run in Fernalla's Revival Plains by heart. That's gotta count for something, right {player}?",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Fernalla's Revival Plains"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_006",
      "text": "Don't go to The Blight alone. Scrubby tried. Three times. Scrubby does not recommend.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["The Blight"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_007",
      "text": "Scrubby finally got a Tarnished Plate Armor! It's tarnished but hey, Scrubby is too. Perfect match!",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_008",
      "text": "Scrubby's Copper Sword broke again. That's the fourth one this week. But copper is cheap and Scrubby is persistent!",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_009",
      "text": "One day Scrubby will wear Golden Plate. Today Scrubby wears a Muddy Jerkin. But one day!",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_010",
      "text": "Hey {player}! Scrubby didn't die today! Well, not yet. The day is young!",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_011",
      "text": "{player}!! Scrubby is so happy to see you! Group with Scrubby? Please? Anyone? ...Scrubby will wait.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_012",
      "text": "Hi {player}! Scrubby just survived a fight! Well, Scrubby ran away, but running is surviving!",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_013",
      "text": "Okay so Scrubby died. Again. But Scrubby lasted two seconds longer this time! Progress! ...Scrubbadub OUT!",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "quirk"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_014",
      "text": "Scrubby's shield broke, sword's dull, and Scrubby is out of potions. Let's do this. Scrubby believes!",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "determination"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "scrubby_015",
      "text": "Watch this! ...okay don't watch that. Pretend you didn't see that. Scrubby is fine. Totally fine.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "quirk"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Scrubby"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_001",
      "text": "The Torchbearers of Brax are a glorified book club. They 'preserve his memory.' I preserve kill counts.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "deity", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_002",
      "text": "The Agents of the Wisp think they can restore Siva. How quaint. I'm sure that'll work out wonderfully.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "deity", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_003",
      "text": "Fernalla's Children are still looking for the Great Willow's Branch. I found better gear while they were praying.",
      "context_tags": ["lore", "deity", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_004",
      "text": "Stowaway's Step. Where all the new dead weight washes ashore. Wonderful. More people to carry.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Stowaway's Step"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_005",
      "text": "Old Krakengard is wasted on the Eldoth Molorai. I could clear that place in half the time they spend posturing.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Old Krakengard"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_006",
      "text": "Underspine Hollow separates the competent from the dead weight. Guess which category most of you fall into.",
      "context_tags": ["zone", "combat", "advice"],
      "zone_affinity": ["Underspine Hollow"],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_007",
      "text": "Oh, you're still using a Cloth Shirt? How... quaint. I've been in Drakescale Cuirass for ages.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_008",
      "text": "Apotheosis dropped for me on the first kill. Some of us are just built different.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_009",
      "text": "I've seen people fight over a Tarnished Halberd like it matters. Pathetic. Farm something real.",
      "context_tags": ["gear", "item", "opinion"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_010",
      "text": "Oh. {player}. You're still here. I assumed you'd have quit by now.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_011",
      "text": "Great. {player} again. I'm not babysitting today. Learn or leave.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 4.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_012",
      "text": "{player}. Fine. You can tag along. Try not to embarrass yourself.",
      "context_tags": ["social", "greeting"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 4.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_013",
      "text": "I carry this group every single day. You're welcome, by the way.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "combat"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_014",
      "text": "That was pathetic. Even by your standards. And your standards are already underground.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "insult"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 5.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    },
    {
      "id": "sparkles_015",
      "text": "I've been playing since launch. Trust me, you're doing it wrong. You're all doing it wrong.",
      "context_tags": ["personality", "elitism"],
      "zone_affinity": [],
      "personality_affinity": [],
      "relationship_min": 0.0,
      "relationship_max": 10.0,
      "channel": ["say"],
      "priority": 1.5,
      "sim_name": "Sparkles"
    }
  ]
}
